07)в”Ӯ         group_by:         в”Ӯ
08)в”Ӯ string_col@0 as string_colв”Ӯ
09)в”Ӯ                           в”Ӯ
10)в”Ӯ           mode:           в”Ӯ
11)в”Ӯ      FinalPartitioned     в”Ӯ
